=== 2019年政治危机 ===
2019年8月，副总理[[馬泰奧·薩爾維尼|马泰奥 · 萨尔维尼]]宣布对[[朱塞佩·孔特|孔戴]]提出不信任动议，加剧了此前多数党内部的紧张局势<ref>{{Cite web|title=La Lega presenta al Senato una mozione di sfiducia a Conte. M5S attacca Salvini: "Giullare"|url=http://www.rainews.it/dl/rainews/articoli/Salvini-Subito-in-Aula-poi-le-elezioni-Conte-Dovra-spiegare-le-ragioni-della-crisi-648408f5-df6c-49f8-bf6d-a73532bd60ab.html|accessdate=2021-01-09|work=rainews|language=it|archive-date=2019-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820183327/http://www.rainews.it/dl/rainews/articoli/Salvini-Subito-in-Aula-poi-le-elezioni-Conte-Dovra-spiegare-le-ragioni-della-crisi-648408f5-df6c-49f8-bf6d-a73532bd60ab.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。许多政治分析人士认为，提出不信任动议是为了迫使提前举行选举，以改善中右翼联盟在议会中的地位，确保萨尔维尼成为下一任总理<ref>{{Cite news|title=Italy's League files no confidence motion in prime minister in bid to trigger election|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2019/08/09/italys-league-files-no-confidence-motion-prime-minister-inbid/|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=2019-08-09|accessdate=2021-01-09|issn=0307-1235|language=en-GB|first=Nick|last=Squires|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826042808/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2019/08/09/italys-league-files-no-confidence-motion-prime-minister-inbid/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

8月20日，在议会辩论中，孔戴严厉指责萨尔维尼是一个政治机会主义者，他”只是为了个人利益而引发政治危机” ，随后向马塔雷拉请辞<ref>{{Cite news|title=Italian PM resigns with attack on 'opportunist' Salvini|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/aug/20/italian-pm-expected-resign-giuseppe-conte|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2019-08-20|accessdate=2021-01-09|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Angela|last=Giuffrida|archive-date=2020-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310043319/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/aug/20/italian-pm-expected-resign-giuseppe-conte|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，马塔雷拉开始与议会团体进行磋商<ref>{{Cite news|title=Italy’s Government Collapses, Turning Chaos Into Crisis (Published 2019)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/20/world/europe/italy-pm-giuseppe-conte-resign.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2019-08-20|accessdate=2021-01-09|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jason|last=Horowitz|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826121315/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/20/world/europe/italy-pm-giuseppe-conte-resign.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在马塔雷拉和议会之间的协商期间，五星运动和[[民主黨_(義大利)|民主党]]之间可能出现了相对多数的信任票<ref>{{Cite web|title=Grasso, possibile intesa M5s-Pd-Leu - Ultima Ora|url=http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/topnews/2019/08/19/grasso-possibile-intesa-m5s-pd-leu_301fb033-f640-4d0f-bba3-ea37eb594c9b.html|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2019-08-19|work=Agenzia ANSA|language=it|archive-date=2019-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819161904/http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/topnews/2019/08/19/grasso-possibile-intesa-m5s-pd-leu_301fb033-f640-4d0f-bba3-ea37eb594c9b.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月28日，民主党领导人[[尼古拉·津加雷蒂|尼古拉 · 津加雷蒂]]宣布他会支持让朱塞佩 · 孔戴继续担任新政府首脑。

次日，马塔雷拉接见了孔戴，挽留并让他继续领导新内阁。9月4日，孔戴宣布了他的新内阁组成，而新一届阁员主要由五星运动和中左翼联盟组成，并于第二天在[[奎里纳莱宫|奎里纳莱宫]]宣誓就职。2019年9月9日，意大利众议院以343票赞成，263票反对，3票弃权通过了对政府的信任<ref>{{Cite web|title=Governo, la Camera vota la fiducia con 343 sì al Conte bis. Proteste della Lega|url=https://www.repubblica.it/politica/2019/09/09/news/governo_conte_fiducia_camera-235548089/|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2019-09-09|work=la Repubblica|language=it|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118203103/https://www.repubblica.it/politica/2019/09/09/news/governo_conte_fiducia_camera-235548089/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=XVIII Legislatura - Lavori - Resoconti Assemblea - Dettaglio sedute|url=https://www.camera.it/leg18/410?idSeduta=0222&tipo=stenografico#sed0222.stenografico.tit00070.sub00030|accessdate=2021-01-09|work=www.camera.it|language=it|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031133247/https://www.camera.it/leg18/410?idSeduta=0222&tipo=stenografico#sed0222.stenografico.tit00070.sub00030|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年9月10日，在参议院的第二轮信任投票中，169名议员投票赞成新政府，133名议员投了反对票<ref>{{Cite web|title=TPR : The Public's Radio : TPR|url=https://thepublicsradio.org/article/italys-new-pro-europe-govt-wins-2nd-confidence-vote|accessdate=2021-01-09|work=thepublicsradio.org|archive-date=2019-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016205409/https://thepublicsradio.org/article/italys-new-pro-europe-govt-wins-2nd-confidence-vote|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Covid-19流行期间 ===
[[File:Mattarella_25_Aprile_2020_2.jpg|缩略图]]
在马塔雷拉担任总统期间，意大利遭受爆发了[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]的打击。2020年2月，意大利成为2019冠状病毒病确诊病例最多的国家之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Coronavirus, Italia prima in Europa per numero di contagi: è caccia ai focolai|url=https://www.ilmessaggero.it/salute/ricerca/coronavirus_italia_prima_contagi_europa-5068457.html|accessdate=2021-01-09|work=www.ilmessaggero.it|language=it|archive-date=2020-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223000631/https://www.ilmessaggero.it/salute/ricerca/coronavirus_italia_prima_contagi_europa-5068457.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2020年12月，已证实超过1,800,000宗冠状病毒个案和66,000宗死亡个案，疫情主要影响[[伦巴第大区|伦巴底]]、[[埃米利亚|埃米利亚]]、[[罗马涅|罗马涅]]、[[威尼托大区|威尼托]]和[[皮埃蒙特大区|皮德蒙特]]等北部大区<ref>{{Cite web|title=Coronavirus, due casi a Milano|url=https://www.corriere.it/cronache/20_febbraio_22/coronavirus-italia-nuovi-contagi-lombardia-veneto-245e72d4-5540-11ea-8418-2150c9ca483e.shtml|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2020-02-22|last=online|first=Simona Ravizza e redazione|work=Corriere della Sera|language=it|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222225105/https://www.corriere.it/cronache/20_febbraio_22/coronavirus-italia-nuovi-contagi-lombardia-veneto-245e72d4-5540-11ea-8418-2150c9ca483e.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2月22日，孔特内阁宣布了一项控制[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒疾病疫情]]的法案，对来自意大利北部11个不同城市的5万多人进行了隔离。并在几天之后，关闭全国的学校和大学。2020年3月8日，意大利政府将隔离措施扩大到整个伦巴底地区和其他14个北部省份，封锁了全国超过四分之一的人口<ref>{{Cite news|title=Coronavirus: Northern Italy quarantines 16 million people|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-51787238|newspaper=BBC News|date=2020-03-08|accessdate=2021-01-09|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414111715/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-51787238|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，政府将实施的隔离措施扩大到全国<ref>{{Cite web|title=All of Italy is in lockdown as coronavirus cases rise|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/09/europe/coronavirus-italy-lockdown-intl/index.html|accessdate=2021-01-09|last=CNN|first=Valentina Di Donato, Emma Reynolds and Rob Picheta|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302234046/https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/09/europe/coronavirus-italy-lockdown-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{Cite news|title=On Day 1 of Lockdown, Italian Officials Urge Citizens to Abide by Rules|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/08/world/europe/italy-coronavirus-quarantine.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-03-08|accessdate=2021-01-09|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jason|last=Horowitz|first2=Emma|last2=Bubola|archive-date=2020-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318171930/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/08/world/europe/italy-coronavirus-quarantine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在当时被描述为人类历史上最大的封锁措施<ref name="#2"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Italy locks down northern region in response to coronavirus outbreak|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/3/7/21169637/italy-lockdown-lombardy-coronavirus-outbreak|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2020-03-07|last=Lyons|first=Kim|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200308071135/https://www.theverge.com/2020/3/7/21169637/italy-lockdown-lombardy-coronavirus-outbreak|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Italy Locks Down Much of the Country’s North Over the Coronavirus|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/07/world/europe/coronavirus-italy.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-03-07|accessdate=2021-01-09|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jason|last=Horowitz|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331193341/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/07/world/europe/coronavirus-italy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=To contain coronavirus, Italy will restrict movement across much of its northern region, including the city of Milan|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/italy-coronavirus-milan-lombardy-lockdowns/2020/03/07/403fcea2-60b3-11ea-ac50-18701e14e06d_story.html|newspaper=Washington Post|accessdate=2021-01-09|issn=0190-8286|language=en-US|first=Chico|last=Harlan|first2=Stefano|last2=Pitrelli|archive-date=2020-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402133344/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/italy-coronavirus-milan-lombardy-lockdowns/2020/03/07/403fcea2-60b3-11ea-ac50-18701e14e06d_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月18日，封锁正式结束，政府允许酒吧、餐馆、理发店和健身房等重新开业<ref>{{Cite web|title=La Fase 2: ecco come l'Italia ripartirà il 18 maggio|url=http://www.rainews.it/dl/rainews/articoli/coronavirus-Fase-2-ecco-come-si-riparte-il-18-maggio-6a0c52c3-2f99-4170-95de-e6d221e7ff21.html|accessdate=2021-01-09|work=rainews|language=it|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118113801/https://www.rainews.it/dl/rainews/articoli/coronavirus-Fase-2-ecco-come-si-riparte-il-18-maggio-6a0c52c3-2f99-4170-95de-e6d221e7ff21.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月3日恢复了在部分地区之间旅行的可行性<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mercoledì cadono i confini delle regioni: si potrà circolare ovunque|url=https://www.corriere.it/cronache/20_maggio_29/3-giugno-via-libera-circolazione-tutte-regioni-3e52429a-a1e1-11ea-972c-41555f8ee621.shtml|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2020-05-29|last=Guerzoni|first=Fiorenza Sarzanini e Monica|work=Corriere della Sera|language=it|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029044434/https://www.corriere.it/cronache/20_maggio_29/3-giugno-via-libera-circolazione-tutte-regioni-3e52429a-a1e1-11ea-972c-41555f8ee621.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2021内阁重組 ===
2021年1月13日，由于联合政府就2019冠状病毒病疫情防控及制定国家复苏计划草案上存在分歧，[[马泰奥·伦齐|马泰奥·伦齐]]宣布[[意大利活力党|意大利活力党]]退出执政联盟，导致孔特政府失去了[[意大利参议院|意大利参议院]]的绝对多数地位。1月18日、19日，孔特政府在[[意大利众议院|意大利众议院]]和[[意大利参议院|意大利参议院]]仅以微弱优势通过信任投票。但由于孔特政府失去了[[意大利参议院|意大利参议院]]的绝对多数地位，若无法获得参议院绝对多数支持，多项政策恐难以获得通过。1月26日，孔特向塞尔焦·马塔雷拉提出辞职。<ref name="#3">{{Cite news|title=Italian PM Conte resigns in split over Covid response|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55802611|newspaper=BBC News|date=2021-01-26|accessdate=2021-02-09|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212133911/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55802611|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#3"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=热点问答：意大利总理孔特为何辞职？-新华网|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-01/27/c_1127028797.htm|accessdate=2021-02-09|work=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126175348/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-01/27/c_1127028797.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月23日，马塔雷拉授權前義大利中央銀行行長及前歐洲中央銀行總裁[[馬里奧·德拉吉|马里奥·德拉吉]]（意大利语：Mario Draghi）組建新一屆內閣政府。<ref>{{Cite web|title=意大利總統授權經濟學家德拉吉組建新政府-香港商報|url=http://www.hkcd.com/content/2021-02/04/content_1247243.html|accessdate=2021-02-09|work=www.hkcd.com|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204083459/http://www.hkcd.com/content/2021-02/04/content_1247243.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 個人生活 ==
他與玛丽萨·基亞澤（Marisa Chiazzese）結婚，後者是[[羅馬法|羅馬法]]學教授，巴勒莫大學[[院长_(学术机构)|院长]]勞羅·基亞澤（Lauro Chiazzese）的女兒。玛丽萨夫人已于2012年逝世。他有3个孩子，<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.panorama.it/news/politica/sergio-mattarella-lato-privato-uomo-misurato/ | title=Sergio Mattarella: profilo privato di un uomo misurato | publisher=Panorama | date=January 30, 2015 | accessdate=January 31, 2015 | language=it | archive-date=2019-12-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231184158/https://www.panorama.it/news/politica/sergio-mattarella-lato-privato-uomo-misurato/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>分別：爲劳拉(在她父亲的总统任期内履行第一夫人的礼仪职能)、弗朗西斯科和贝尔纳多二世。.

